<div class="px-4 py-8">
  <div class="text-center mb-8">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">모아봄</h1>
    <p class="text-lg text-gray-600">가족 아기 사진첩</p>
  </div>

  <% unless logged_in? %>
    <div class="max-w-md mx-auto">
      <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-6">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">우리 아이의 소중한 순간,<br>가족과 함께 모아봄</h2>

        <div class="space-y-3">
          <%# Apple 로그인 (미구현) %>
          <a href="#" class="block w-full bg-black text-white text-center py-3 rounded-lg font-medium opacity-50 cursor-not-allowed pointer-events-none">
            🍎 Apple로 계속하기
          </a>

          <%# 카카오 로그인 (활성화) %>
          <%= link_to "/auth/kakao", class: "block w-full bg-yellow-400 text-gray-900 text-center py-3 rounded-lg font-medium hover:bg-yellow-500 transition-colors" do %>
            💬 카카오로 계속하기
          <% end %>

          <%# Google 로그인 (미구현) %>
          <a href="#" class="block w-full bg-white text-gray-900 text-center py-3 rounded-lg font-medium border-2 border-gray-300 opacity-50 cursor-not-allowed pointer-events-none">
            📧 Google로 계속하기
          </a>
        </div>

        <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 text-center mt-4">
          로그인 시 이용약관 및 개인정보 처리방침에 동의하게 됩니다.
        </p>

        <% if Rails.env.development? %>
          <div class="mt-6 pt-4 border-t border-gray-200">
            <%= button_to "🚀 개발 모드로 빠른 진입", dev_login_path, method: :post, class: "w-full bg-purple-600 text-white text-center py-3 rounded-lg font-medium hover:bg-purple-700 transition-colors" %>
            <p class="text-xs text-gray-400 text-center mt-2">개발 환경 전용</p>
          </div>
        <% end %>
      </div>
    </div>
  <% else %>
    <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto">
      <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-6 mb-4">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">환영합니다!</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600">로그인되었습니다.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-6 text-center">
          <div class="text-4xl mb-2">📷</div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900">사진</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mt-1">아직 사진이 없어요</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-6 text-center">
          <div class="text-4xl mb-2">👨‍👩‍👧</div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900">가족</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mt-1">가족을 초대하세요</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  <% end %>
</div>
